videos.description: Daniel Gafford races down the court to reject Malik Dunbar's layup on the fast break.
videos.headline: Gafford denies Dunbar on fast break

videos.description: Daniel Gafford punishes the rim on two dunks and Daryl Macon slams one home shortly after for the Razorbacks.
videos.headline: Arkansas throws down 3 huge slams in 1 minute

videos.description: Daniel Gafford continues to excel around the rim with another huge two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Gafford cannot be stopped in the paint

videos.description: Daniel Gafford throws down two more dunks at the beginning of the second half to keep Arkansas rolling against No. 14 Auburn.
videos.headline: Gafford stays hot early in the second half

videos.description: At home on senior night, Daniel Gafford shines off the bench dropping a team-high 21 points and Jaylen Barford impresses with 20 points of his own to lead the Razorbacks to a 91-82 win over the No. 14 Tigers.
videos.headline: Arkansas earns upset on senior night

videos.description: Daniel Gafford was unstoppable in the paint in a 91-82 victory over No. 14 Auburn.
